function.name: abs.Expression
function.arg:
<%@ livebos language='javascript' %>
var fhbz = ABS_SQLVALUE("select paramvalue from jgcrm.tsysparam  where paramname='ams.system'");
var fhz=true;
if(fhbz==0){
  fhz=true;
}else{
  var bean = ABS_LOADBEAN("com.apex.bss.mod.ibb.systemdocking.apexsoft.livebosbean.TaskEndBean");
  var result = bean.perform($Login.User.UserID,O_WORKFLOW.InstID);
  var code = result.get('O_CODE');
  var note = result.get('O_NOTE');
  if(code > 0){
      ABS_SETRETNOTE(note);
     fhz= true;
   }else{
      ABS_SETRETNOTE(note);
      fhz= false;
   }
}
fhz;

condition.arg: <%@ livebos language='javascript' %> (O_WORKFLOW.CJSHYJ2==1 && ABS_SQLVALUE("select paramvalue from jgcrm.tsysparam where paramname='ams.system'") == 0)||(O_WORKFLOW.ZKBSFYYJ==1 && ABS_SQLVALUE("select paramvalue from jgcrm.tsysparam where paramname='ams.system'") == 1)

function.name: abs.Expression
function.arg:
<%@ livebos language='javascript' %>
var fhbz = ABS_SQLVALUE("select paramvalue from jgcrm.tsysparam  where paramname='ams.system'");
var fhz=true;
if(fhbz==0){
  fhz=true;
}else{
  var bean = ABS_LOADBEAN("com.apex.bss.mod.ibb.systemdocking.apexsoft.livebosbean.TaskEndBean");
  var result = bean.perform($Login.User.UserID,O_WORKFLOW.InstID);
  var code = result.get('O_CODE');
  var note = result.get('O_NOTE');
  if(code > 0){
      ABS_SETRETNOTE(note);
     fhz= true;
   }else{
      ABS_SETRETNOTE(note);
      fhz= false;
   }
}
fhz;
